h=\Big\{ \begin{bmatrix}x & y\\y & x\end{bmatrix}:  x^2-y^2=1 \Big\};
g=\Big\{ \begin{bmatrix}x & y\\-y & -x\end{bmatrix}:  x^2-y^2=1 \Big\}.
\phi = \Big\{ \begin{bmatrix}x & y\\y & x\end{bmatrix}\cup \begin{bmatrix}x & y\\-y & -x\end{bmatrix}\ :  x^2-y^2=1 \Big\}?
